The operation of staffing agencies has not been immune to the Covid-19 situation, as the downturn in tourism has led to a downturn in the construction sector, and these two sectors have been the most active in using staffing agencies' services.
Nevertheless, the residents of Dunhaga 18 seemed to have plenty to do and hung their work clothes and gloves in the common area to dry after a long day of work in the rain.
It should be noted that despite the terrible state of the house, the apartment that the boys shared appeared to be reasonably well maintained.
When the reporter bade the Romanian boys farewell, the irony suddenly hit him: In the best location in Reykjavík, a 1,500 square meter property is in a state of disrepair.
The owners want to improve the house and the neighbors want to improve the condition, but they disagree on the definition of "improvement."
In the middle sits the city's planning department, a victim of endless appeals and complaints in the planning process and a slow-moving resolution by the Environmental and Resources Tribunal.
The house is then inhabited by Romanian workers, perhaps just those who come to improve the situation when the Icelanders stop arguing.
